sourceList.expandedForm: Identifies the type of change made to this version of the Code (i.e., changes from the prior version published in "CDT-2011-2012"), with the following meanings: 30 = No change to existing code, nomenclature or descriptor; 31 = New procedure code and nomenclature, and descriptor, if present; 35 = Revision in the nomenclature or descriptor (or both), or to indicate a revision to an entire subcategory.
